              <history-note id="DLM1956663"><amended-provision>Section 141(1)(h)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>added</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>3 April 2009</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM1098345">section 25(5)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Corrections Amendment Act 2009</amending-leg> (2009 No 3).</history-note>
