              <history-note id="DLM1956690"><amended-provision>Section 182(6)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>repealed</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>3 April 2009</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM1098380">section 32(6)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Corrections Amendment Act 2009</amending-leg> (2009 No 3).</history-note>
