          <heading>Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971 (1971 No 53)</heading>
          <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
            <text><emphasis style="italic">Amendment(s) incorporated in the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM401069">Act(s)</extref></citation></emphasis>.</text>
          </para>
