    <skeletons id="DLM2642712">
      <skeleton.act act.no="59" id="DLM2642713" type="public" year="2009">
        <skeleton.act.cover>
          <title>Corrections (Contract Management of Prisons) Amendment Act 2009</title>
          <assent>2009-12-07</assent>
          <commencement>see section 2</commencement>
        </skeleton.act.cover>
        <skeleton.act.body prov-type="section">
          <prov id="DLM2642700" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
            <heading>Title</heading>
            <prov.body>
              <subprov skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="yes" denominator="yes"/>
                <para>
                  <text>This Act is the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM1888300">Corrections (Contract Management of Prisons) Amendment Act 2009</extref></citation>.</text>
                </para>
              </subprov>
            </prov.body>
          </prov>
          <prov id="DLM2642701" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
            <heading>Commencement</heading>
            <prov.body>
              <subprov skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="yes" denominator="yes"/>
                <para>
                  <text>This Act comes into force on the day after the date on which it receives the Royal assent.</text>
                </para>
              </subprov>
            </prov.body>
          </prov>
          <part act.no="59" act.type="public" date.as.at="2009-12-07" date.assent="2009-12-07" date.first.valid="2009-12-08" date.instructed="2009-02-17" id="DLM2642702" in.amend="false" instructing.office="Corrections" irdnumbering="no" stage="in-force" toc="yes" year="2009">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
            <heading>Transitional provision and consequential amendments</heading>
            <prov id="DLM2642703" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">7</label>
              <heading>Transitional matters</heading>
              <prov.body>
                <subprov skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>Any transfer of the management of a prison between the department and a contractor does not affect the completion of a matter or thing that relates, or the bringing or completion of proceedings that relate, to an existing right, interest, title, immunity, or duty.</text>
                  </para>
                </subprov>
                <subprov skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>Despite subsection (1), the contractor and the chief executive, in the name and on behalf of the Crown, may make any arrangements that they consider necessary or desirable to determine the respective liabilities of the Crown and the contractor in relation to any matter referred to in subsection (1).</text>
                  </para>
                </subprov>
              </prov.body>
            </prov>
          </part>
        </skeleton.act.body>
      </skeleton.act>
    </skeletons>
    <end.reprint-note id="DLM2251806">
      <reprint.index>
        <heading>Contents</heading>
        <para>
          <list>
            <item>
